g into V4 to verify the hints are complete—I've got event:confirm, event:listen, 確認ダイアログ, イベントアクション, and several others all accounted for, but I'm noticing some gaps like title属性, target属性, and the component paths confirm.tag and dialog.tag that appear in the attribute table but aren't yet in the hints list.\n\nLooking at the attributes table more carefully, I see title, message, condition, target, stop, and revert as the main properties, but the hints only cover message, condition, stop, and revert—missing title and target. Also, event_alert is referenced in the components table and could be useful for users searching for related components.\n\nSo the main finding here is that V4 is missing those two attribute names from the hints, which is a minor gap. Everything else checks out cleanly without any fabrications or inaccuracies in how the content was described.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":2,"cache_creation_input_tokens":13964,"cache_read_input_tokens":18400,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":13964,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":8},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"d1db2155-9b64-4799-b717-67302ce3e967","uuid":"e2314e19-4ecc-4e73-9c89-08608a5abc0f"}
